<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Tags</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select tags from the drop-down list or enter the first 3 letters of the tag’s name to have some suggestions displayed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Whisper</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">If you click on the button <strong>Whisper</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-eye  "></i></span> <span class="icon red"><i class="fa fa-toggle-off  "></i></span>), only those employees who have rights for the messenger can read the message. Your contacts are not able to see the message. Whisper mode is active if the button looks like this: <span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-eye-slash  "></i></span> <span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-toggle-on  "></i></span>.<br>
<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> If <strong>Whisper</strong> is activated (<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-eye-slash  "></i></span> <span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-toggle-on  "></i></span>), the field <strong>Minutes</strong> and the button <strong>Billable</strong> are deactivated.</p></td>
