<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Delete</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Click on <span class="icon red"><i class="fa fa-minus-square  "></i></span> to delete the entire message stream.<br>
<strong><em>Important:</em></strong> Upon deletion, the main message and all related messages are deleted.</p></td>
