<h2 id="delete-message">5. Deleting a message</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Click on <span class="icon red"><i class="fa fa-minus-square  "></i></span> in the open message to delete the entire message stream.<br>
<strong><em>Important:</em></strong> The main message and all related messages are deleted.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Before you delete the message stream irretrievably, a window is shown where you have to confirm that you want to delete the message.</p>
</div>
</div>
